## Falsifier preregister (C-axis)

- **F-Q-1** (closed): H₂/STO-3G/parity-mapped E0 within chemical accuracy. PASS (selftest A4 F3 + smoke).
- **F-Q-1-spectroscopic** (closed): same, within spectroscopic accuracy (≤ 1 µHa). PASS (smoke 0.4 µHa).
- **F-Q-2** (closed 2026-05-07): LiH/STO-3G/R=1.5Å chemical accuracy. Best delta = 1.408 mHa via depth=2 hardware-efficient ansatz + HF init prefix |0011⟩ + multi-restart 5 seeds. 4/5 in band [1.4, 2.0] mHa, 1 stuck @ 12.9. See docs §24.
- **F-Q-3** (closed 2026-05-07): H2 bond-length scan reproduces equilibrium R_eq + dissociation curve within chemical accuracy. **Actual measurement: 11/11 points sub-µHa, max |Δ|=0.8 µHa, mean 0.4 µHa, R_eq match exact (0.740 Å == FCI), E_min(VQE) − E_min(FCI) = 0.2 µHa**. depth=1 + HF init + seed=42. See docs §25.
- **F-Q-4** (closed 2026-05-06): live ANU end-to-end. PASS: hexa-bio adapter pull --bytes 8 --live → provenance="anu_legacy" tier="anu-legacy" (T1.a, qrng.anu.edu.au) bytes_hex="5f8b2ee823e965cb". qmirror secret-chain fallback chain landed paid/trial/free 키 부재 → legacy 자동. See docs §22.
- **F-Q-5** (closed 2026-05-06): long-lived bridge wall reduction ≥ 5×. n=15 re-bench measured **31.39×** (fresh 163.41s vs pool 5.21s; pool per-call **0.35s**), 6× threshold 초과 PASS. See docs §18.8.
- **F-Q-6** (open): drug-target fragment. Awaits C cycle.

raw#10 honest C3 (cycle-26 closure):

1. mock LCG 결정성으로 multi-restart 다양성 검증 미완 (B3 live ANU 후 진정 검증).
2. qmirror python bridge 가 매 호출 cold-start (~1.8 s). long-lived bridge (B4) 까지는 perf 한계.
3. spectroscopic accuracy 결과는 seed=42 single-run; repeat-variance 측정 미완 (별도 sweep production).
4. cross-repo SSOT (consumers += hexa-bio in `nexus/.roadmap.qmirror`) uncommitted; nexus 세션에서 commit 분리.
